Gometz-la-Ville

Gometz-la-Ville is a city in Île-de-France, in France.

GPS Coordinates of Gometz-la-Ville, Île-de-France, France

Gometz-la-Ville is located on the latitude of 48.67219 and longitude of 2.12868 and has a geohash of u09sbkw01cff.

Cities and Towns near Gometz-la-Ville

The nearest significant population center from Gometz-la-Ville is Droue-sur-Drouette in Centre-Val de Loire, France, located 32 kilometers or 20 miles ↙ SW of the city. Other locations in close proximity include Auneau (Centre-Val de Loire, France) located 34 km (21 mi) ↙ SW and Aunay-sous-Auneau (Centre-Val de Loire, France) located 34 km (21 mi) ↓ S of Gometz-la-Ville.
